        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "Here he again paused to search for the much needed stick, found one suited to his purpose, and by its aid succeeded in decreasing still more the drain upon his life current; yet could not stop the flow entirely.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72200_000005_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72200/7285_72200_000005_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "Leaving the path, he plunged deeper into the woods, ran for some distance along the edge of a swamp, and leaping in up to his knees in mud and water, doubled on his track, then turned again, and penetrating farther and farther into the depths of the morass, finally climbed a tree, groaning with the pain the effort cost him, and concealed himself among the branches.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72200_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72200/7285_72200_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "His pursuers came up to the spot where he had made his plunge into the water; here they paused, evidently at fault.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72200_000006_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72200/7285_72200_000006_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "He could hear the sound of their footsteps and voices, and judge of their movements by the gleam of the torches many of them carried.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72200_000007_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72200/7285_72200_000007_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "Some now took one direction, some another, and he perceived with joy that his stratagem had been at least partially successful.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72200_000007_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72200/7285_72200_000007_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "One party, however, soon followed him into the swamp.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72200_000007_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72200/7285_72200_000007_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "He could hear Spriggs urging them on and anathematizing him as \"a scoundrel, robber, burglar, murderer, who ought to be swung up to the nearest tree.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72200_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72200/7285_72200_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "Every thicket was undergoing a thorough search, heads were thrown back and torches held high that eager blacks eyes might scan the tree tops, and Jackson began to grow sick with the almost certainty of being taken, as several stout negroes drew nearer and nearer his chosen hiding place.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72200_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72200/7285_72200_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "He uttered a low, breathed imprecation upon his useless right arm, and the man whose sure aim had made it so.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72200_000011_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72200/7285_72200_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "The search was kept up for some time longer, with no light but an occasional flash from the skies; but finally abandoned, as we have seen.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72200_000012_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72200/7285_72200_000012_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "Jackson passed several hours most uncomfortably and painfully on his elevated perch, quaking with fear of both man and reptile, not daring to come down or to sleep in his precarious position, or able to do so for the pain of his wound, and growing hour by hour weaker from the bleeding which it was impossible to check entirely.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72200_000013_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72200/7285_72200_000013_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "Perhaps he had now two new murders on his hands; he did not know, but he had at least attempted to take life, and the story would fly on the wings of the wind; such stories always did.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72200_000014_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72200/7285_72200_000014_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "He must contrive a plausible story, and go to him; at break of day, before the news of the attack on Viamede would be likely to reach him.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72200_000014_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72200/7285_72200_000014_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "It would be a risk, but what better could be done?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72200_000015_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72200/7285_72200_000015_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "The storm had spent itself before the break of day, and descending from his perch with the first faint rays of light that penetrated the gloomy recesses of the swamp, he made his way out of it, slowly and toilsomely, with weary, aching limbs, suffering intensely from the gnawings of hunger and thirst, the pain of his injury, and the fear of being overtaken by the avengers of his innocent victims.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72200_000016_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72200/7285_72200_000016_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "The man reeled as he walked, either from intoxication or weakness and fatigue.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72200_000017_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72200/7285_72200_000017_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "With the assistance of Nap's strong arm, the man tottered in, then sank, half fainting, into a chair.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72200_000018_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72200/7285_72200_000018_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "\"A glass of wine, Nap, quick!\" cried the doctor, sprinkling some water in his patient's face, and applying ammonia to his nostrils.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72200_000020_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72200/7285_72200_000020_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "\"Food, for the love of God,\" he gasped.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72200_000020_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72200/7285_72200_000020_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "\"I'm starving!\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72200_000021_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72200/7285_72200_000021_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "\"Bread, meat, coffee, anything that is on the table, Nap,\" said his master; \"and don't let the grass grow under your feet.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72200_000024_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72200/7285_72200_000024_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "You haven't strength for talk just now.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72200_000025_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72200/7285_72200_000025_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "dr Balis had his own suspicions as he ripped up the coat sleeve, bared the swollen limb, and carefully dressed the wound; but kept them to himself.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72200_000025_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72200/7285_72200_000025_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "The stranger's clothes, though much soiled and torn in several places by contact with thorns and briers, were of good material, fashionable cut, and not old or worn; his manners were gentlemanly, and his speech was that of an educated man.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72200_000026_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72200/7285_72200_000026_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "\"Is that mortification?\" asked the sufferer, looking ruefully at the black, swollen hand and fore arm, and wincing under the doctor's touch as he took up the artery and tied it.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72200_000029_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72200/7285_72200_000029_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "\"Oh yes; neither the bone nor nerve has suffered injury; the ball has glanced from the bone, passed under the nerve, and cut the humeral artery. Your tourniquet has saved you from bleeding to death.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72200_000029_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72200/7285_72200_000029_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "'tis well you knew enough to apply it.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72200_000030_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72200/7285_72200_000030_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "The doctor's task was done.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72200_000030_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72200/7285_72200_000030_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "Nap had set a plate of food within reach of the stranger's left hand, and he was devouring it like a hungry wolf.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72200_000031_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72200/7285_72200_000031_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "I can't deny that things look suspicious.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72200_000032_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72200/7285_72200_000032_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "\"No; a party of us, from New Orleans last, came out to visit this beautiful region.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72200_000032_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72200/7285_72200_000032_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "We were roaming through a forest yesterday, looking for game, when I somehow got separated from the rest, lost my way, darkness came on, and wondering hither and thither in the vain effort to find my comrades, tumbling over logs and fallen trees, scratched and torn by brambles, almost eaten up by mosquitos, I thought I was having a dreadful time of it.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72200_000033_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72200/7285_72200_000033_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "The doctor listened in silence, his face telling nothing of his thoughts.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72200_000034_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72200/7285_72200_000034_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "\"A bad business,\" he said, rising and beginning to draw on his gloves. \"You are not fit to travel, but are welcome to stay here for the present; had better lie down on the sofa there and take a nap while I am away visiting my patients.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72200_000034_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72200/7285_72200_000034_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "Nap, clean the mud and blood from the gentleman's clothes; take his boots out and clean them too; and see that he doesn't want for attention while I am gone.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72200_000034_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72200/7285_72200_000034_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "Good morning, sir; make yourself at home.\" And the doctor walked out, giving Nap a slight sign to follow him.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72200_000035_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72200/7285_72200_000035_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "\"Nap,\" he said, when they were out of ear shot of the stranger, \"watch that man and keep him here if possible, till I come back.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72200_000037_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72200/7285_72200_000037_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "Nap went back into the office while the doctor mounted and rode away.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72200_000038_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72200/7285_72200_000038_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "have you been house breaking or some other mischief?\" dr Balis was traveling in the direction of Viamede, intending to call there too, but having several patients to visit on the way, did not arrive until the late breakfast of its master and mistress was over.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72200_000039_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72200/7285_72200_000039_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "They were seated together on the veranda, her hand in his, the other arm thrown lightly about her waist, talking earnestly, and so engrossed with each other and the subject of their conversation, that they did not at first observe the doctor's approach.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72200_000042_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72200/7285_72200_000042_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "\"No, uncle, what is it?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72200_000047_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72200/7285_72200_000047_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "\"A murderer, sir; one whose object was to take my husband's life,\" Elsie answered with a shudder, and in low, tremulous tones, leaning on Edward's arm and gazing into his face with eyes swimming with tears of love and gratitude.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72200_000048_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72200/7285_72200_000048_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "\"My wife's also, I fear,\" mr Travilla said with emotion, fondly stroking her sunny hair.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72200_000050_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72200/7285_72200_000050_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "\"No; his ball passed over our heads, grazing mine so closely as to cut off a lock of my hair.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72200_000052_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72200/7285_72200_000052_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "\"A flash of lightning showed us to each other and we fired simultaneously, I aiming for his right arm.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72200_000053_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72200/7285_72200_000053_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "\"You had him pursued promptly, of course?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72200_000054_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72200/7285_72200_000054_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "\"Yes; but they did not find him.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72200_000054_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72200/7285_72200_000054_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "I expected to see them return with his corpse, thinking he must bleed to death in a very short time.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72200_000055_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72200/7285_72200_000055_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "I'd better return at once, lest he should make his escape.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72200_000056_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72200/7285_72200_000056_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "\"I do; I can,\" replied mr Travilla.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72200_000056_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72200/7285_72200_000056_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "\"But, my little wife, how you are trembling!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72200_000057_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72200/7285_72200_000057_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "\"The man's name is Tom Jackson; he is a noted gambler and forger, has been convicted of manslaughter and other crimes, sent to the penitentiary and pardoned out.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72200_000058_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72200/7285_72200_000058_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "\"I must hurry home and prevent his escape.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72200_000058_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72200/7285_72200_000058_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "Why, it's really dangerous to have him at large.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72200_000060_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72200/7285_72200_000060_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "\"But how could you tell where it entered or where it passed out, doctor?\" inquired Elsie.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72200_000061_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72200/7285_72200_000061_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "Why, where it goes in it makes merely a small hole; you see nothing but a blue mark; but a much larger opening in passing out, often tearing the flesh a good deal; as in this case.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72200_000063_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72200/7285_72200_000063_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "\"Don't take the trouble, doctor,\" said mr Travilla; \"we will mount and follow you at once, to identify him if he is to be found.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72200_000063_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72200/7285_72200_000063_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "Shall we not, wife?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72207_000001_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72207/7285_72207_000001_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "\"Calm me, my God, and keep me calm While these hot breezes blow; Be like the night dew's cooling balm Upon earth's fevered brow.\" --H.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72207_000003_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72207/7285_72207_000003_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "\"Dear old auntie! to think how hard at work for her country she is, while I sit idle here,\" sighed Elsie, closing the letter after reading it aloud to the assembled family.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72207_000003_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72207/7285_72207_000003_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "\"Mamma, papa, Edward, is there nothing we can do?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72207_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72207/7285_72207_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "\"I think you can,\" was the simultaneous reply; mr Travilla adding, \"and we can help with the lint, and by running the sewing machines.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72207_000005_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72207/7285_72207_000005_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "I'd be glad to add to the comfort of the poor fellows on both sides.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72207_000007_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72207/7285_72207_000007_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "\"And I can send that!\" Elsie exclaimed joyously",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72207_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72207/7285_72207_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "Several busy weeks followed, and a large box was packed and sent off.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72207_000016_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72207/7285_72207_000016_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "\"Yes,\" he said, gently taking it from her, \"but rather too valuable a plaything for my little pet.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72207_000018_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72207/7285_72207_000018_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "\"I gave her leave to look over the contents of my jewel box; she is a very careful little body, and mammy and I are both on the watch:\" answered mamma.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72207_000021_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72207/7285_72207_000021_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "\"Let papa see where you put it, precious,\" he said, following her as she tripped across the room and seated herself on a cushion in front of the box.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72207_000022_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72207/7285_72207_000022_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "\"Dere, papa, dus where Elsie dot it,\" she said, laying it carefully back in its proper place.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72207_000023_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72207/7285_72207_000023_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "\"Little wife, your jewels alone are worth what to very many would be a handsome fortune.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72207_000025_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72207/7285_72207_000025_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "\"No, it is a good investment; especially as things are at present.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72207_000030_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7285/72207/7285_72207_000030_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7285",
        "content": "Mamma, may I, too?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7285_72207_000038_000001",
